      </h1>

      <div id="about" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="font-medium text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">
          <a
            href="https://thisux.com"
            target="_blank"
            class="underline underline-offset-2"></a>A CSE undergrad focused on
          Full Stack Development. I build with Node.js, Go, and Rust while
          exploring system design and Devops Tools.
        </div>

        <div class="font-medium text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Currently Working on
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-5">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/Kshitijknk07/DiagramX"
              target="_blank"
              class="p-3 rounded-lg gap-2 flex-wrap hover:rotate-1 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-[#1F1F1F] dark:hover:bg-[#2F2F2F]"
            >
